import React from "react";
import { Card, Button, Container, Spinner } from "react-bootstrap";
import netflix from "../images/Netflix.png"
import disney from "../images/disney+hotstar.png"
import Amazon from "../images//Amazon-Prime.webp"

function BootstrapApp() {

    return (

        <>
            <Container>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={netflix} className="img-fluid" />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Title>Netflix</Card.Title>
                        <Card.Text align="justify">
                            React-Bootstrap replaces the Bootstrap JavaScript. Each component has been built from scratch as a true React component, without unneeded dependencies like jQuery.
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Button variant="primary">Watch Here</Button>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>

                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={netflix} className="img-fluid" />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Title>Dis</Card.Title>
                        <Card.Text align="justify">
                            React-Bootstrap replaces the Bootstrap JavaScript. Each component has been built from scratch as a true React component, without unneeded dependencies like jQuery.
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Button variant="primary">Watch Here</Button>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>

                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={netflix} className="img-fluid" />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Title>React Bootstrap</Card.Title>
                        <Card.Text align="justify">
                            React-Bootstrap replaces the Bootstrap JavaScript. Each component has been built from scratch as a true React component, without unneeded dependencies like jQuery.
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Button variant="primary">Watch Here</Button>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}


export default BootstrapApp;
